reviewText: Great episode! It is a 40 minute episode not a 20 minute one. It shows how dog, Tim and leland deal with their first case since they were arrested for the Andrew luster case. If you have seen the special on the arrest this follows on to his first case. Would definitely recommend it!
never seen this before ordering it.i never new that dog and his brother and son go to jail,it was so sad..i am so glad that i own this now.
